{
  "id": "guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale",
  "title": "Format data based on locale",
  "contents": "\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"format-data-based-on-locale\" translation-result=\"on\">根据语言环境格式化数据<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"format-data-based-on-locale\">Format data based on locale<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 提供了以下内置的数据转换<a href=\"guide/glossary#pipe\" title=\"pipe - Glossary | Angular\">管道</a>。数据转换管道会使用 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> 标记来根据每个语言环境的规则来格式化数据。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular provides the following built-in data transformation <a href=\"guide/glossary#pipe\" title=\"pipe - Glossary | Angular\">pipes</a>.  The data transformation pipes use the <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> token to format data based on rules of each locale.</p>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"><p translation-result=\"on\">数据转换管道</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Data transformation pipe</p></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><p translation-result=\"on\">详情</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Details</p></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" title=\"DatePipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>DatePipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><p translation-result=\"on\">格式化日期值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Formats a date value.</p></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" title=\"CurrencyPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>CurrencyPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><p translation-result=\"on\">将数字转换为货币字符串。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Transforms a number into a currency string.</p></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\" title=\"DecimalPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><p translation-result=\"on\">将数字转换为十进制数字字符串。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Transforms a number into a decimal number string.</p></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" title=\"PercentPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>PercentPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><p translation-result=\"on\">将数字转换为百分比字符串。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Transforms a number into a percentage string.</p></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\" translation-result=\"on\">使用 DatePipe 显示当前日期<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\">Use DatePipe to display the current date<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要以当前语言环境的格式显示当前日期，请对 <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 使用以下格式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To display the current date in the format for the current locale, use the following format for the <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code>.</p>\n\n<!--todo: replace with code-example -->\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n{{ today | <a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">date</a> }}\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\" translation-result=\"on\">改写 CurrencyPipe 的当前语言环境<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\">Override current locale for CurrencyPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">将 <code>locale</code> 参数添加到此管道以覆盖 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 标记的当前值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Add the <code>locale</code> parameter to the pipe to override the current value of <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> token.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要强制货币使用美式英语 ( <code>en-US</code> )，请以如下格式使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code> </p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To force the currency to use American English (<code>en-US</code>), use the following format for the <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code></p>\n\n<!--todo: replace with code-example -->\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n{{ amount | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a> : 'en-US' }}\n\n</code-example>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><strong>注意</strong>：为 <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code> 指定的语音环境设置会覆盖应用程序的全局 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 标记。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>NOTE</strong>: The locale specified for the <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code> overrides the global <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> token of your application.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" translation-result=\"on\">下一步是什么<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"whats-next\">What's next<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare templates for translations | Angular\">准备翻译模板</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare templates for translations | Angular\">Prepare templates for translations</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 2021/10/28</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriodRules\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriods\n - api/common/registerLocaleData\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n - guide/pipes\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/PercentPipe\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/glossary#pipe\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#whats-next\n - guide/i18n-common-prepare\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"
